OL,6,FA take-at-home tablet for multiple
OL,7,Fsclerosis (MS) is set to be more
OL,8,Fbroadly rolled out on the NHS,
OL,9,Fpotentially benefiting thousands of
OL,10,Fpatients in England.
OL,12,FThe move will also "significantly free
OL,13,Fup clinical time" by reducing the need
OL,14,Ffor hospital appointments, officials
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FThe health service is thought to be
OL,18,Fthe first in Europe to widely rollout
OL,19,Fcladribine, also known as Mavenclad
OL,20,Fand made by Merck.
