OL,3,CTake-at-home tablet for MS approved by
OL,4,CNHS
OL,6,FIt is taken for 20 days spread over
OL,7,Ffour years, reducing the need for
OL,8,Fhospital visits and extensive
OL,9,Fmonitoring.
OL,11,FCladribine was previously only
OL,12,Frecommended for patients with severe,
OL,13,Fhighly active MS.
OL,15,FThe latest rollout is expected to
OL,16,Fbenefit about 2,000 people over the
OL,17,Ffirst three years.
OL,19,FWomen with MS who want to conceive
OL,20,Fwill also be able to safely do so.
