OL,6,FHealth minister Ashley Dalton added:
OL,7,F"We know that patients with
OL,8,Fneurological conditions such as
OL,9,Fmultiple sclerosis face immense
OL,10,Fchallenges, so I am delighted that
OL,11,Fthis decision means more patients will
OL,12,Fget access to a treatment that will
OL,13,Fgreatly improve their quality of life.
OL,15,F"By expanding access to medicines that
OL,16,Fcan be taken at home, we can shift
OL,17,Fcare out of hospitals and into the
OL,18,Fcommunity, giving patients more
OL,19,Ffreedom and saving the NHS money.
